                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18271025-128-victim676 t18271025-128-viclabel746"></join>. The prisoner lived with me twice, but only two months the last time. On the 1st of September I gave him two 10l. and one 5l. notes, to go to Messrs. Combe and Delafield's, to get silver, where he had been several times before; I never saw him again till last Saturday. but I was on the look out. I have not recovered a farthing of the property.</p>
